full_text: Just so we’re clear: Madeleine Albright didn’t say this to spark female empowerment. She said it specifically to shame female Democrats who chose Bernie Sanders in the 2016 primary. I won’t trash a dead woman, but I won’t bend reality for her either. https://t.co/3bazHnhtuk
